headline: Merger Shockwave: Performance Food Group and US Foods Walk Away From a $31 Billion Power Play
summary: An industry-defining deal collapses overnight as both distributors pivot back to standalone strategies and fresh buybacks.

headline: Performance Food Group, US Foods Scrap Merger Talks
summary: Performance Food Group and US Foods Holdings have called off talks to merge in a deal that would have created a food-distribution giant rivaling top player Sysco
